Adhipati

420.
1303Adhipatipaccayā nahetuyā dasa, naārammaṇe satta, naanantare dasa, nasamanantare dasa, nasahajāte satta, naaññamaññe aṭṭha, nanissaye satta, naupanissaye satta, napurejāte dasa, napacchājāte dasa, naāsevane dasa, nakamme dasa, navipāke dasa, naāhāre dasa, naindriye dasa, najhāne dasa, namagge dasa, nasampayutte aṭṭha, navippayutte satta, noatthiyā satta, nonatthiyā dasa, novigate dasa, no avigate satta. (23)
